data.description: Fort Bend area growing rapidly! This 2 Story home features 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. It boasts a 1st-floor primary suite with double vanity, large shower, and walk-in closet and tub.  The spacious kitchen has been freshly painted with "Swiss Coffee" by Sherwin Williams. It has 52" cabinets & Granite Countertops, Texas-size eat-in Island, and Stainless appliances.  There is a spacious upstairs living space perfect for a media room. The backyard has a covered patio & an additional Gazebo with Lights on a slab and a storage shed. The home has a new whole-home generator and a water softener that will be conveyed with the property, in addition to recessed lighting around the full exterior. The community amenities aren't to be missed: Splash pad, playground, soccer, basketball courts & walking trails. This beautiful home is priced to sell quickly!
